f=Executive Office/vista/marketplace/north-star-metric/assets/nsm_spec_template.md · h1:North Star Metric Specification=**Team Product:** [Team name] **Author(s):** [PM, exec sponsor, data lead] **Date:** [YYYY-MM-DD] **Review cadence:** Quarterly **Status:** [Draft Approved production] · h2:2. Five-test scorecard=\| Test \| Pass? \| Notes \| · h2:2. Five-test scorecard=\|------\|-------\|-------\| · h2:2. Five-test scorecard=\| Customer value: NSM up = customer got more value \| [Yes/No] \| \| · h2:2. Five-test scorecard=\| Strategic alignment: matches how we make money \| [Yes/No] \| \| · h2:2. Five-test scorecard=\| Leading, not lagging: predicts long-term success \| [Yes/No] \| \| · h2:2. Five-test scorecard=\| Single number: one dashboard tile \| [Yes/No] \| \| · h2:2. Five-test scorecard=\| Movable: team can affect within a quarter \| [Yes/No] \| \| · h2:4. Leading indicators=input, 2-3 indicators move BEFORE input does. · h3:Input 1: [name]=[Leading indicator moves far advance?], [Leading indicator 2], [Leading indicator 3] (optional) · h3:Input 2: [name]=[Leading indicator 1], [Leading indicator 2], [Leading indicator 3] (optional) · h3:Input 3: [name]=[Leading indicator 1], [Leading indicator 2] · h3:Input 4: [name] (optional)=[Leading indicator 1], [Leading indicator 2] · h3:Input 5: [name] (optional)=[Leading indicator 1], [Leading indicator 2] · h2:6. Counter-metrics (business protection)=\| Counter-metric \| Threshold \| Current \| Owner \| · h2:6. Counter-metrics (business protection)=\|----------------\|-----------\|---------\|-------\| · h2:6. Counter-metrics (business protection)=\| [Metric] \| [e.g., "must stay above 18%"] \| [value] \| [name] \| · h2:8. OKR alignment=\| OKR Key Result \| Which input it moves \| · h2:8. OKR alignment=\|----------------\|----------------------\| · h2:8. OKR alignment=\| [KR1] \| [Input #] \| · h2:8. OKR alignment=\| [KR2] \| [Input #] \| · h2:8. OKR alignment=\| [KR3] \| [Input #] \|